      "actionDate": "2025-05-05",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in Senate",
      "text": "<p><strong>Jocelyn Nungaray National Wildlife Refuge Act</strong></p><p>This bill renames the Anahuac National Wildlife Refuge located in Anahuac, Texas, as the Jocelyn Nungaray National Wildlife Refuge.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2025-07-01T20:16:27Z",
      "versionCode": "00"
    },
    {
      "actionDate": "2025-07-24",
      "actionDesc": "Public Law",
      "text": "<p><strong>Jocelyn Nungaray National Wildlife Refuge Act</strong></p><p>This act renames the Anahuac National Wildlife Refuge located in Anahuac, Texas, as the Jocelyn Nungaray National Wildlife Refuge.</p><p>The act provides statutory authority for <a href=\"https://www.federalregister.gov/documents/2025/03/10/2025-03869/honoring-jocelyn-nungaray\">Executive Order 14229</a>, which also renamed&nbsp;the refuge as the Jocelyn Nungaray National Wildlife Refuge.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2026-06-15T19:09:14Z",
      "versionCode": "49"
    }
